\par\pard\plain \tx0\tx360\tx720\tx1080\tx1440\tx1800\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\fi360\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93What about your people, though? Couldn\u8217\'92t you move elsewhere, to some other river?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Laughs like he\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92d said the most ridiculous thing.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93It\u8217\'92s telling that you didn\u8217\'92t ask, \u8216\'91Why didn\u8217\'92t you fight back?\u8217\'92.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Well, how could you? This is the Hrks we\u8217\'92re talking about.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93It\u8217\'92s not human.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93We give names to dogs.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Dogs have feelings and empathy. All the Mazydai have is the capacity to know, but they can\u8217\'92t understand. They\u8217\'92ll never understand why we do what we do, or why we feel so strongly about things that they consider best left unremembered.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Walking}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Eh, I\u8217\'92m still going to call him Obo. He\u8217\'92s too cleaver to not have a name.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93If it were clever, we wouldn\u8217\'92t have been able to ambush it like it were a rat.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93How did you manage to ambush him?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93With ease.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93But how? Obo can practically see through rocks. He can smell things from miles away. Remember when we were in that pit cave, and he said there were Hrks coming? He knew before your scout did.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Mazydai can\u8217\'92t see through rocks.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93How do you know?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Because if he could, he wouldn\u8217\'92t have been ambushed.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Maybe. Ehh, maybe I shouldn\u8217\'92t say.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Say what?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Obo is\u8230\'85Obo is a deceitful person. Like, no doubt he\u8217\'92s listneing in right now, . Every time you see him and he looks like he\u8217\'92s sleeping or unconscious, he\u8217\'92s not, he\u8217\'92s awake.\u8221\'94 }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Mandri shook his pack to see if he could get Obo to stir, but Obo\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s head just bobbled side to side, before coming to rest in a dead man\u8217\'92s hang.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93?\u8221\'94}
